Package org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation

Class AbstractXYAnnotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.NativeObjectContainer
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.AbstractNode
        • org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation.AbstractAnnotation
          • org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation.AbstractXYAnnotation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IsDefaultsAnnotation, IsDefaultsXYAnnotation
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BoxAnnotation, EllipseAnnotation, LineAnnotation
    abstract class AbstractXYAnnotation
extends AbstractAnnotation
implements IsDefaultsXYAnnotation
    Implements a annotation which can be configured with the X (min and max) and Y (min and max) values, like BoxAnnotation and LineAnnotation.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
